data.description: Beazer Homes Silverado floor plan in the master planned community of Wellington. This single-story home features 3 beds, 2 baths, study, covered patio plus 2-car garage! The kitchen includes upgraded stainless steel appliances and a large island. The family room creates a perfect open space for entertaining and includes a cozy fireplace. The primary suite features a walk-in closet. The primary bathroom includes a walk-in shower, soaking tub and dual vanity sinks. *Days on market is based on start of construction.*
